text: Antônio Eliseu Zuqueto (April 29, 1929 - August 23, 2016) was a Brazilian Roman Catholic bishop. Ordained to the priesthood in 1955, Zuqueto served as bishop of the Roman Catholic Diocese of Teixeira de Freitas–Caravelas, Brazil, from 1983 to 2005. ==See also== *Roman Catholicism in Brazil ==Notes== Category:1929 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Brazilian Roman Catholic bishops
title: Antônio Eliseu Zuqueto
